        "html": "<div class=\"beautiful-template-stage\" data-template-slug=\"peoples-platform\">\n<section class=\"s-cover grain beautiful-template-slide active\" data-screen-label=\"01 Cover\">\n  <div class=\"frame\"></div>\n  <div class=\"meta-top\">\n    <div class=\"pill\">Q2 · 2026</div>\n    <div>STRATEGIC REVIEW · INTERNAL</div>\n    <div class=\"pill\">VOL. 01</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"center\">\n    <div class=\"title\">QUARTERLY<br/>REVIEW</div>\n    <div class=\"row2\">\n      <div class=\"for\">a</div>\n      <div class=\"sub\">PRESENTATION TEMPLATE</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"footline\">\n    <span>PREPARED BY THE TEAM</span>\n    <span class=\"dot\"></span>\n    <span>MAY 2026</span>\n    <span class=\"dot\"></span>\n    <span>VERSION 01</span>\n  </div>\n</section>\n</div>",
